  "detailed_description": "<i>A new game from the creator of NIX UMBRA.</i><br><br>ENTER THE QUANTUM CRYSTAL DIMENSION. Take control of a state-of-the-art rover to mine alien energy trapped inside the intracrystalline multispace.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948220/extras/cbc37827c5b908d97134898c2dee6e13.poster.avif?t=1660907665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948220/extras/cbc37827c5b908d97134898c2dee6e13.webm?t=1660907665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948220/extras/cbc37827c5b908d97134898c2dee6e13.mp4?t=1660907665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Experience unique first-person perspective inside crystals.<br></li><li> Pilot a cutting-edge surgical multidirectional rover equipped with high-res laser sensors.<br></li><li> 8 extraterrestrial crystal types.<br></li><li> Procedural generated levels that will test your spatial memory capacity.<br></li><li> Quasi-infinite procgen ambient soundscape.<br></li><li> Opaque game mechanics.</li></ul><br><strong>AMD GPUs not supported at the moment.</strong>",
